rules: Rule1: Either the publication is recalled, or if the vehicle is not compliant then the vehicle is not licensed.
Rule2: Either the vehicle is audited or alcohol is inspected.
Rule3: When alcohol is inspected, the publication is not recalled.
Rule4: The financial product is reviewed or the publication is examined.
Rule5: Whenever the publication is examined, if the vehicle is audited then the publication is not recalled.
Rule6: Given that the vehicle is renewed, alcohol is not expired.
Rule7: Either the publication is contested, or if it is not the case that renewed vehicle implies expired alcohol, then the financial product is not pending.
Rule8: If alcohol is certified, then whenever alcohol is approved, the financial product is compliant.
Rule9: Either the financial product is accredited or alcohol is certified.
Rule10: In the event that the publication is validated, the financial product is not accredited.
Rule11: Should the vehicle be authorized, alcohol is permitted.
Rule12: Provided that alcohol is permitted, the financial product is cleared.
Rule13: Whenever the financial product is cleared, the publication is disputed.
Rule14: Under the condition that the financial product is compliant, the vehicle is not licensed.
Rule15: In the event that alcohol is supervised, the vehicle is monitored.
Rule16: If the financial product is endorsed, then provided that alcohol is approved, alcohol is supervised.
Rule17: Should the publication be registered, the financial product is compliant.
Rule18: Whenever the vehicle is monitored, the publication is registered.
Rule19: If the financial product is investigated, then under the condition that alcohol is approved, the publication is registered.
Rule20: In the event that the publication is restricted, the publication is not banned.
Rule21: If it is not the case that reviewed financial product implies audited vehicle leads to not recalled publication, then the vehicle is renewed.
Rule22: Provided that it is not the case that renewed vehicle implies expired alcohol, the financial product is pending.
Rule23: Should it not be true that approved alcohol implies monitored vehicle, then alcohol is suspended.
Rule24: If it is not the case that cleared financial product implies not disputed publication, then the vehicle is resolved.
Rule25: Provided that it is not the case that cleared financial product implies not disputed publication, the vehicle is not resolved.
Rule26: In the event that it is not the case that either the publication is sanctioned or the financial product is endorsed, then the vehicle is terminated.

Rule27: If it is not the case that not not not investigated financial product implies restricted publication leads to appealed vehicle implies overturned alcohol, then the financial product is finalized.

Rule28: Provided that it is not the case that not not not investigated financial product implies restricted publication leads to appealed vehicle implies overturned alcohol, the financial product is not finalized.
Rule29: In the event that the publication is not validated, the vehicle is authorized.
Rule30: Provided that the financial product is not investigated, the publication is banned.
Rule31: If the vehicle is not compliant, then the vehicle is licensed.
Rule32: Provided that the vehicle is not compliant, alcohol is approved.
facts: Fact1: The vehicle is not appealed.
Fact3: The publication is not contested.
Fact4: The publication is not sanctioned.
Fact5: The vehicle is not terminated.
